query:
SELECT id, name, 
CASE WHEN mapImageUrl IS NULL THEN 'NULL'
     WHEN mapImageUrl = '' THEN 'EMPTY'
     ELSE SUBSTRING(mapImageUrl, 1, 80)
END as mapUrl
FROM shopping_centres 
WHERE name LIKE '%Highlands%';
